name: Jumpman (Tronic Verlag)
overview: Published in Computronic 1986/05-06, Pixel No.37 (10/1987), Digital Marketing PD #221 / a.k.a. "The Wheel" which is reminiscent of BC's Quest for Tires, but the object is as simple as a stone, just keep on rolling down the line and jump any obstacles to keep the wheels turning.
